----------CEPH-MEDIC â€“ FIND COMMON ISSUES IN CEPH CLUSTERS--------------


Requirements:

A fresh cluster with 3 MONs, N OSDs,optionals(N RGWs,N MGRs,N MDSs) with user with sudo permissions.

For one TC, cluster with 1 among 3 MONs, should be collocated with one OSD.

Specify the cluster name while running the test scripts.

Example: sudo python ceph-medic_cli_validation.py -cluster name_of_cluster

if cluster name is ceph ,just run sudo python ceph-medic_cli_validation.py
